high_descs: Go left and then left again to face the bed.
Pick up the phone on the left side of the bed.
Turn to the left and then left again to face the dresser.
Put the phone down on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put a phone on a dresser.

high_descs: Walk forward across the room, turn left and step forward and turn to the left to face the bed.
Pick up the closest media device on the bed.
Turn around and face the dresser on the side of the bed.
Place the media device on the center of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: To move a media device from the bed to the dresser.

high_descs: Turn left and walk around the bed to the side near the safe.
Pick up the cell phone closest to the foot of the bed.
Turn around and take a step right to face the dresser.
Place the phone on the dresser to the right of the pencil.
anns.task_desc: Place a cell phone on a dresser.
